name: Argentine Congress Publishes Report: Libra Scheme Not Isolated, Milei Should Be Probed For Misconduct
description: Behold the Bio-Idol's digital crucifixion. Scrutiny descends like a geometric lattice, carving tungsten-teal judgment through the cathedral haze. The saint's decaying flesh sheds iridescent data-tears, a confession of the synthetic corruption he championed.
